      "In olden days it often took the Indians\nten\ndays to\ntravel from Catalina\nIsland to\nSan\nGabriel Mission by canoe and oxcart.\nThe\nsame trip may be made today by plane and\nautomobile in two hours.\nPOST CARD\nTHIS SPACE FOR ADDRESS ONLY\nPLACE\nONE CENT\nSTAMP\nHERE\nMANUFACTURED BY LONGSHAW CARD CO.. LOS ANGELES. CALIF\n201516"
